Subject: [PATCH v2 ethtool]: add json support for base command
Date: Fri, 19 Jul 2024 10:55:44 +0200
Message-Id: <20240719085544.2337393-1-f.pfitzner@pengutronix.de>
X-Mailer: git-send-email 2.39.2
